'''嗅感器'''（{{lang-en|'''Tömösváry organs'''，亦作'''temporal organs'''或'''postanntennal organs'''}}<ref>{{cite book|last1=Gordh|first1=G.|last2=Headrick|first2=D.H.|title=A Dictionary of Entomology|date=2009|publisher=CABI|location=Wallingford|isbn=9781845935429|page=979|edition=2nd|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=9IcmCeAjp6cC&pg=PA979#v=onepage&q&f=false}}</ref>）是一個由[[匈牙利|匈牙利]][[博物學家|博物學家]]及[[馬陸學家|馬陸學家]]{{link-en|Ödön Tömösváry|Ödön Tömösváry}}在1883年所發現的感覺器官，存在於大多數的[[馬陸|馬陸]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Millipedes |2= |url=https://www.fieldmuseum.org/sites/default/files/intromillipedchinese.pdf |language=en |accessdate=2015-12-08 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120440/https://www.fieldmuseum.org/sites/default/files/intromillipedchinese.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>及部份[[蜈蚣|蜈蚣]]和[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]物種，位於頭部[[觸角|觸角]]的基部，包含一個盤狀結構以及一個被感覺細胞包圍的中央孔，它們可能用來感應振動，甚至提供聽覺<ref name=IZ>{{cite book |last=Barnes |first=Robert D. |year=1982 |title=Invertebrate Zoology |publisher=Holt-Saunders International |location=Philadelphia, PA |pages=810–816 |isbn=0-03-056747-5}}</ref>，但其實其具體功用我們到現在還未能詳細掌握<ref name="Biology of Centipedes">{{cite book|last=Lewis|first=J. G. E.|title=The Biology of Centipedes|year=2008|publisher=[[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]]|location=Cambridge|isbn=9780521034111|pages=110–111|edition=Digitally printed 1st paperback version.}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Sierwald|first1=Petra|last2=Bond|first2=Jason E.|title=Current Status of the Myriapod Class Diplopoda (Millipedes): Taxonomic Diversity and Phylogeny|journal=Annual Review of Entomology|date=2007|volume=52|issue=1|pages=401–420|doi=10.1146/annurev.ento.52.111805.090210|pmid=17163800}}</ref>。所以嚴格來講，「嗅感器」這個譯名其實不大準確。

